            </p>
            <div class="solution-grid">
                <div class="solution-item">
                    <h4>Automated Invoice Processing</h4>
                    <p>Digital invoice capture with OCR technology, automatic matching with purchase orders, and intelligent approval routing based on amount and vendor type.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-item">
                    <h4>Integrated Payment System</h4>
                    <p>Automated payment scheduling with early payment discount calculations, electronic payment processing, and automated vendor notifications.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-item">
